title: André Moes
text: André Moes (2 March 1930 – 13 November 2019) was a Luxembourgian <a href="cycle%20sport">cyclist</a>. He competed in the <a href="Cycling%20at%20the%201952%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Men%27s%20individual%20road%20race">individual</a> and <a href="Cycling%20at%20the%201952%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Men%27s%20team%20road%20race">team road race</a> events at the <a href="1952%20Summer%20Olympics">1952 Summer Olympics</a>.
